name: Universe #212
description: Universe #212 - The universe of reflections, Noko, gathered the light from all the other universes. The green sun helped it see and reflect anything it gathered and reflect back. As the sun started to lose it's power, 212 helped it's rejuvanation. With that kind of sudden energy, it reflected all it had stored to 212. With it, 212 became the universe and the universe became 212.
